## Swimming

---



[Entity Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_condition_types/swimming)

Checks whether the entity is currently swimming (in the swimming pose).

Type ID: `origins:swimming`



---

### üìù Note

__This entity condition type will only work on players.__






---

### Examples

```json
"condition": {
    "type": "origins:swimming"
}
```
